  "remarks": "Public Prosecutor of the Pervomaiski District of Minsk. He dealt with the case of Dmitri Bondarenko. The accusation presented by him has a clear and imminent political motivation and it is a clear violation of the Code of Criminal Procedure. It is based on wrong classification of the events of 19 Dec 2010, not sustained by evidences, proofs and testimonies of witnesses.",
